{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Sets whether to show alert for push notifications when app is in foreground."}],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"+ (","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:v","text":"void"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setShowPushnotificationAlert:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"text":"BOOL","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@BOOL","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"show","kind":"internalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"parameters":[{"name":"show","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"YES to show alerts in foreground, NO to suppress them (default)"}]}]}],"kind":"parameters"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","text":"Discussion","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"By default, iOS does not display notification banners when the app is in the foreground.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Enable this to show system notification alerts even when the app is active."}]},{"anchor":"Example","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Example"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Configure based on app type:"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["class NotificationConfigManager {","","    func configureForAppType(_ appType: AppType) {","        switch appType {","        case .messaging:","            \/\/ Messaging apps typically handle notifications in-app","            Pushwoosh.configure.setShowPushnotificationAlert(false)","","        case .ecommerce, .news:","            \/\/ E-commerce and news apps benefit from showing all notifications","            Pushwoosh.configure.setShowPushnotificationAlert(true)","","        case .game:","            \/\/ Games might want to suppress during gameplay","            Pushwoosh.configure.setShowPu